    "Understanding these complexities is crucial for forecasting, managing, and mitigating the impacts of such hazards.",
    "To effectively evaluate the risks posed by coastal threats, a comprehensive approach to Earth Systems science is imperative.",
    "The project seeks to develop a convergent scientific strategy that bridges the gap between coastal sustainability, human engagement, and coastal dynamics.",
    "A significant aim of this initiative is to create an undergraduate curriculum centered on coastal ecosystems at three study sites: Belize, the US Virgin Islands, and Miami, Florida.In alignment with this overarching goal, the present paper explores the practical application of Artificial Intelligence (AI), conducting a detailed comparative analysis of ChatGPT and Google Gemini's performance in addressing environmental science education queries.",
    "This analysis focuses on their utility, precision, and educational value within the context of coastal ecosystem education."
